STATE
v.
Dexter Durane HENRY. No. 9P15-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Aug. 20, 2015. Teresa M. Postell, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Dexter Durane Henry, for Henry, Dexter Durane. Susan I. Doyle, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 5th of January 2015 by Defendant to Proceed In Forma Pauperis:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference, this the 20th of August 2015."
